{
  "stem": "22047.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were-- I think they did that on purpose so that we would-- we would just relish getting into combat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed there about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were ordered to load up on boxcars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And for six days, we were in these 40-and-8 boxcars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were just-- we were stacked so full-- so many people per car that all of us couldn't lie down at once, so we had to take turns lying down or sitting down.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it took us six days to get there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got to Lyon, France, which was just a little east of Nancy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we disembarked there and we were trucked to-- actually to Strasbourg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in December of-- actually, we went into a fort on the Maginot Line initially.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were-- this was just before Christmas of 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we spent Christmas Eve and Christmas night in this fort, and we had a turkey dinner.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We felt very strange, though.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here we are.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're in-- in-- in this place, but we're not in combat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when are we going to be in combat?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then we only spent I think three days there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were trucked to Strasbourg, France and quartered in a military school for about three more days, and then to a-- a chateau on the banks of the Rhine River.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our job was-- this is an absolutely gorgeous chateau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I showed you a booklet of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed there about a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would send patrols out to a-- it was actually a tower that we went up in to observe the enemy across the river.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
